<plot>A has-been radio personality spends the later years of his career hosting an midnight radio horror show he has no respect for. Callers tune in and relate their personal brushes with the supernatural, meanwhile Jaime La'Faite and Lazaro, the shows producer, make fun of the callers. However one night they are faced with what might be their first actual contact with the supernatural, and are forced to question just how much responsibility their jobs actually entail. All of this while a life hangs in the balance.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?310346</url></doc>
